{
  "texts": [
    "One reason that this is concerning is that applicants with fewer financial resources may not be able to afford to access GPT-4 and may, instead, rely on the free ChatGPT which uses GPT-3.5.",
    "Thus, while examining GPT-3.5's performance may not provide insight into a LLM's full potential, it provides insight into how the majority of candidates relying on a LLM might perform on tests.",
    "Indeed, as discussed above, GPT-4 has two advantages over the earlier version.",
    "First, it is trained on more data.",
    "Second, it is a larger neural network."
  ]
}